Instructions
1.Log in to your WordPress admin panel.
2.Navigate to Appearance → Theme File Editor.
3.Open style.css and paste the code from your style.css file at the very bottom.
4.Open functions.php and paste the code from your functions.php file at the very bottom.

That’s it! You should now see product prices displayed in BGN and EUR on your site.

Notes:
The exchange rate used is 1.95583 BGN = 1 EUR.
These are custom functions. We take no responsibility for any issues or inaccuracies that may occur.

